  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Will you be able to survive to the next floor?</h2><br><strong>NEXT FLOOR is a score attack, fast-paced, ultraviolent fps, with a lot of guns and blood, where your objective is simple, get out of an elevator, cross a floor full of enemies, traps and explosives until you reach the next elevator.</strong><br><br><strong>Enemies that want to take you down at any cost, but don't worry because using your creativity, you can:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/b4e77ed1b5fff515787738707bcd62b7.poster.avif?t=1705548086\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/b4e77ed1b5fff515787738707bcd62b7.webm?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/b4e77ed1b5fff515787738707bcd62b7.mp4?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Traps </strong>that you can use to finish enemies in the most interactive ways possible<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/d2d0f5b9da0509724c15d881c6db02af.poster.avif?t=1705548086\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/d2d0f5b9da0509724c15d881c6db02af.webm?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/d2d0f5b9da0509724c15d881c6db02af.mp4?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>And explosives,</strong> to obliterate everything you see in front of you and make everything even more cinematic..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/37ffd23bfe7d7a4de439f70266cd53f9.poster.avif?t=1705548086\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/37ffd23bfe7d7a4de439f70266cd53f9.webm?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/37ffd23bfe7d7a4de439f70266cd53f9.mp4?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Featuring a series of <i>weapons (one more violent than the other), different types of kicks, slow motion, lots of violence, a hook to pull enemies and even teleportation</i>, take all your stress out on enemies and make the <strong>most creative kills to get as many points as possible</strong>, and of course, <strong>reach the highest floor you can</strong>, however, with each floor, the enemies become increasingly stronger and more deadly.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Death is your playground</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/e0aaa265e68355c7359220cfca0054c5.poster.avif?t=1705548086\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/e0aaa265e68355c7359220cfca0054c5.webm?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677650/extras/e0aaa265e68355c7359220cfca0054c5.mp4?t=1705548086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Given this, answer me, how far can you get?</h2></strong>",
